				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">How Dare You!?<a name="61898"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Sep 14 04 3:56 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Do not make fun of a rapier.  A rapier will disembowel you more quickly than a giant axe or a long sword.
<br />

<br />
A rapier in the hands of a skilled fencer will be the end of an enemy before the enemy is aware of a threat.
<br />

<br />
A rapier says, &quot;we have class, we are educated, and we quick&quot;.  That's what a bard is to me.  Sharp.  Sophisticated.  Deadly.
<br />

<br />
</span></td>
